<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.4">
<l>paruṅkai yāṉaiyiṉ kompiṉaip paṟittataṉ pākaṉaic cāṭippuk</l>
<l>koṟuṅka mallaraik koṉṟupiṉ kañcaṉai yutaittava ṉuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>karumpi ṉūṭuyar cālikaḷ viḷaitaru kaḻaṉiyil malivāvi</l>
<l>maruṅke lāmpoḻi lōṅkiya nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the one who, having plucked out the tusk</l>
<l rend="indent">of the thick-trunked elephant, killing its driver,</l>
<l>Having entered [the arena], after slaying the wrestlers all at once,</l>
<l rend="indent">kicked Kaṁsa,</l>
<l>Is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr where groves grow high</l>
<l rend="indent">on all sides of a teeming stepwell,</l>
<l>In the fields where paddy, which rises between the sugarcane,</l>
<l rend="indent">ripens effortlessly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
